                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hay</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Tower</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-01-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 6, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hay advises Mr. Tower of the receipt of the British reply accepting the
                    negotiation if Venezuela assents to conditions imposed by Great Britain, and
                    appointing the British ambassador to confer with Mr. Bowen in Washington.)</p>
            </div>
